{"tid":2496984,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"I.O.I將於5月4日舉行出道5周年紀念直播《I.5.I – Yes, I love it!》","createTime":"2021-04-20T07:48:48.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-01T13:09:34.000Z","uid":219225,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"35b4130360b5378015bec23e23266340280fba1f","tid":2496984,"uid":219225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T07:48:48.000Z","msg":"《I.5.I &ndash; Yes, I love it!》是紀念與粉絲們約定「五年」的直播節目，在組合名中加入「5」，也包含了出道五周年的意義。 特別是 I.O.I 的官方問候《Yes, I love it!》作為主打歌，讓期待 I.O.I 再聚在一起 5 年的粉絲們心動不已。<br />\n<br />\n2016 年通過 Mnet《PRODUCE 101》第一季成團後，在一起1年的 I.O.I 成員們在各自的位置上展開活躍活動，不知不覺 I.O.I 出道 5 年，終於回應粉絲們的等待。<br />\n<br />\nI.O.I 在 2017 年最後一次活動當時留下了「5年後重新組合」的承諾，粉絲們持續等待了 5 年。為了報答粉絲們，慶祝出道 5 周年，決定在出道日的 5 月 4 日舉辦《I.5.I &ndash; Yes, I love it!》，時隔 5 年再次回到粉絲身邊的 I.O.I ，將在 5 月 4 日下午7點通過 kt olletv、seezn、TVING 進行免費直播。"},{"pid":"4e4a1d1ceb11fc7bdcaa269fbbe0f22ae8553415","tid":2496984,"uid":46435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T07:53:04.000Z","msg":"推到5月4!!"},{"pid":"8c0bef635c8a4a09290843f5ae961be686b6ed21","tid":2496984,"uid":219225,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T07:53:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmb6gvYa9DoE9pFqWdKr5PJYZHocbZMg8gRSgDkvDejA45?filename=R3184TO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR3184TO.jpg&h=8a560842&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmSseCikwwQasrPgh34gBggEhEZys7VaNyv2YPBKwDgmK4?filename=zCZOksg.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzCZOksg.gif&h=ad88575a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a60ebb00b8858c0f637c5b1a3432cb0b0439b0e1","tid":2496984,"uid":219225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4e4a1d1ceb11fc7bdcaa269fbbe0f22ae8553415","tid":2496984,"uid":46435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T07:53:04.000Z","msg":"推到5月4!!"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T07:53:39.000Z","msg":"斬<img src=